ve it down!','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7753,'My powers have returned and you have squandered your chance, foolish mortals. Till we meet again.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7754,'With Algernon to keep me supplied, I can do all my work here without hunting for a single herb. If I never have to see the wonders of nature again, it won\'t be too soon.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7755,'I have no more knowledge to bestow upon you. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Herbert Halsey. He is a Forsaken who can teach you more advanced techniques.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7756,'If you seek to become my student, you\'ll need to complete an assignment for me. Prove yourself worthy, and I might even consider rewarding you.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7757,'I\'m not amused by your audacity in coming to me for training. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Martin Felben. He is a Forsaken who can teach you the basics.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7758,'Here to learn? Very well. I suppose you can\'t cause our allies much harm if I teach you. Just as long as you actually do manage to harm our enemies.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7759,'','This potion seems to heal less damage every time I brew it, though I use the same ingredients. There can be only one conclusion: the plants are changing. I cannot say why or into what.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7760,'','It is time you moved on to a more advanced teacher. In the Feathermoon Stronghold of Feralas dwells the night elf Kylanna Windwhisper. She has a brilliant mind; doubtless she can train you further.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7761,'','This is excellent work. Are you ready to undertake a mission on my behalf? I know of no one more qualified.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7762,'','Your skill at brewing potions needs to be greater before you can become one of my students. In the meantime, perhaps Sylvanna Forestmoon or Milla Fairancora can help you, just over there.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7763,'','Your education is progressing well. You should be proud of your accomplishments.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7764,'My colleagues and I are gathering the deadliest substances we know and testing their effects on our enemies. Once I have everything I need, I shall brew such plagues as this world has never seen.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7765,'Incredible. Your potions display a knowledge that rivals my own. I cannot train you further, but talk to the orc Rogvar of Stonard in the Swamp of Sorrows. He\'s known for his cutting-edge experiments.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7766,'You\'ve got real talent and a passion for making potions. There is one little matter I\'d like you to take care of, though.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7767,'You don\'t yet have the skill to study with me. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben over there, or go up the ramp to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. They are Forsaken who can give you the training you need.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7768,'Ready for training? Then try to keep up, $n. We\'ve got a lot of ground to cover.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7769,'','Once I welcomed darkness, for it was the sister of night. Now it is dark all the time, even during the day, and the forests cry out for sustenance. Unless we act soon, this spreading blight will cover the world.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7770,'','Have you come here for instruction in the art of making potions? You were mistaken if you thought that I would offer such a privilege to you, unearned. Go, and do not return to me until you have greater skill.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7771,'','Your skill displays an enduring affection for our art, but I would see further evidence of your commitment. I shall charge you with a task. Fulfill it, and I will be content.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7772,'','Elune has seen fit to gift me with skill and experience. Now I shall pass them on to you.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7773,'Kalaran, I have misplaced my torch. I require another.','Kalaran, I have misplaced my torch. I require another.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(