 just a matter of mastering the techniques for working with leather. Good thing Simon\'s a real sport about helping me learn them.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7950,'There\'s nothing I can teach you, other than maybe a better eye for color and detail. Talk to Simon Tanner over there; he knows a lot of advanced techniques for working with leather.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7951,'This outfit really brings out the blue in my eyes, don\'t you think? It should be obvious I have plenty of skill to go around, so I can afford to share a few of my tricks of the trade. Listen up, okay?','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7952,'','Welcome to our home, $n. Radnaal and I have little to offer, but you are welcome to what hospitality we can provide.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7953,'','My apologies, but you have already learned everything I know. The night elf Faldron could offer you further training, however. Look for him in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7954,'','You need to make your stitches smaller, $n. Fewer items will slip out of your quivers and ammo pouches. Besides, no one likes a lumpy tunic.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7955,'','If you\'re interested in sewing with leather, you\'ve certainly come to the right place. Faldron and Telonis are true artists, and I hope to learn much from them.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7956,'','Oh, I\'m sorry, but you know more about leather than I do at this point. Talk to Faldron over there if you wish to learn more.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7957,'','It\'s so exciting to be here in Darnassus, surrounded by talented people! I just know I\'m going to make my family proud. Maybe if I\'m really lucky, the Sentinels will ask me to join their forces on the front!',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7958,'','This hide isn\'t ready to work with yet. I wish it didn\'t take so long to make leather. There has to be some way to cut down on all this waiting. It can\'t be good for my health, you know?',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7959,'','Aww, what rotten luck! My skills aren\'t good enough to be of any use to you. Oh well. Talk to Fimble Finespindle over there by the loom. He\'s been working with leather for longer than I have.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7960,'','Oh, goody, something else to do while I wait! You\'re a real life-saver, $n!',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7961,'','You like the rug? I killed and skinned the beast myself. May all the centaur fall as easily.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7962,'','I have nothing more to teach you. Talk to Karolek if you wish to further your leatherworking skills.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7963,'','Too bad we can\'t skin the humans and their allies. All that skin is just going to waste. Still, who\'d want to wear the flimsy leather you could make out of it?',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7964,'','Skin, glorious skin. It holds your insides... in. You might\'ve noticed my skin\'s not doing so well. To think I used to worry about my pores. Hardly any skin left to worry about these days. In a way, it\'s very freeing.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7965,'','You\'ve got the hang of it. I can\'t teach you any more, but talk to Arthur Moore, a Forsaken who works in the Rogues\' Quarter of the Undercity. Tell him I sent you.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7966,'','Before the plague came, I knew nothing about leather. Now I know enough to teach others. Death\'s left me with a lot of time on my hands.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7967,'Meat, skin, bones... a good hunter lets nothing go to waste. Every scrap of leather can be salvaged, perhaps to reinforce an ally\'s armor. Thus, each of us is strong alone, but together we become invincible.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7968,'You have outgrown any teachings I could offer. Go with the blessing of the Earth Mother. Seek out the tauren Tarn in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. Be guided by his wisdom.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7969,'We live and die, and the land remains, eternal, unmoved by our passage. Thus, land cannot belong to us, $n. Instead, we belong to it. Therefore we protect the land, for without it we cannot hope to survive.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7970,'The caverns below us are a source of strange and wondrous hides, but you must take care if you venture into their depths, $n. Remember that your own skin is far more valuable.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7971,'Your understanding of leather is deeper than my own. Perhaps you should visit the tauren Krulmoo Fullmoon in Camp Taurajo of the Barrens. He has much knowledge to offer a student of your talents.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7972,'Even here in the wilds, you seek out learning. Your drive for knowledge is an admirable trait.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7973,'Cairne himself lives here, they say. Once I have finished crafting a fitting gift, I will seek him out. Perhaps he will have words of wisdom for me.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7974,'Your talent is beyond my own, friend. Speak with Tarn here; his knowledge of leather is much greater than mine. I\'m sure he would welcome another student.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7975,'Cleanse your hands before you begin any project. Staining the leather with blood or dirt would take away from its natural beauty.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7976,'When I clawed my way out of the grave, I thought my family would welcome me with open arms. Instead, they drove me from the village, screaming in a language I could no longer understand.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7977,'I can\'t help you; your work is beyond my own. Talk to Arthur Moore, over there by the coffins. He\'ll be able to train you further.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7978,'Take every word I say and commit it to memory. Until our enemies have been eradicated, we must never shirk a chance to further our knowledge. Reinforce your armor, and never relax your guard.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7979,'HELP! ASSASSINS HAVE COME TO KILL ME!','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7980,'I\'m free!  That device shall never torment me again!','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7983,'','You are beyond my limited abilities. Seek out the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She can teach you more. I only wish that I could go with you.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7984,'','You were wise to seek me out. I would ask a small favor. In return, there is much I can teach you.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7985,'','My teachings would be too advanced for you at this stage. If you wish to learn more of potions, speak with Tel\'Athir here instead.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7986,'','Listen carefully, $n, for I have much knowledge to impart.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7987,'Even I have my limitations! Go talk to Lavinia Crowe in Undercity if you wish to further your training.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7988,'Not bad... I suppose training you is not out of the question. Very well! Let\'s begin...','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7989,'Randal\'s a bit of a dandy, but he\'s dependable, which is more than I can say for a lot of the students I take on. Still, I guess I can\'t blame them for wanting a bit of adventure.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7990,'Sorry, but you\'ve reached the limit of what I can teach. If you want to learn more, go see Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He\'s pretty talented, so I hear.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7991,'Okay, I\'ll teach you, but I want you to do something for me. This is important, so pay close attention.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7992,'Come back to me when you\'ve had more training. Randal Worth over there can help you with that.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7993,'Hmm, I guess I can take on another student. Well, don\'t just stand there. Tell me what you\'re looking to learn.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7994,'Darianna shows promise, but she is so full of energy that it is hard for her to stay still and listen. With her strength and agility, I fear it won\'t be long before she is called to fight. We must teach her quickly.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7995,'If you are here for further training, you have overestimated my abilities. Have a word with Telonis over there; he can help you.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7996,'This war has been an enormous drain upon our people and resources. Even here on Teldrassil, we cannot escape its repercussions. Forgive me for asking it of you, but would you perform a task for me?','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7997,'In time you will be ready for what I have to teach, $n. Until then, please ask Darianna over there to help you with your training.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7998,'Many animals lost their lives so that we could gain these materials. Do not take their sacrifice lightly, $n. Handle the leather with the respect it deserves.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(7999,'Lots to do! Haven\'t been this busy since my cousin accidentally vaporized all the cloth and leather in Gnomeregan. My, it was drafty for a while! Ah, $n, those were the days....','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8000,'Nope, can\'t help you, I\'m afraid. Your skills have mine beat! If you want to learn more, talk to the night elf Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He\'s amazing!','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8001,'I can see that you\'ll be a quick learner. That\'s good for me, because I\'m always busy these days. In fact, that reminds me: could you run a quick errand for me?','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8002,'Well, I declare! It\'s a new student! I\'ll gladly teach you everything I know once you have a little more skill. Go talk to Gretta Finespindle over there, would you? She\'ll have you up to speed in no time.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8003,'Your skills are coming along nicely. Soon you\'ll be running a leather shop of your own. I\'ll be glad for the help, $n. My hands are only so fast, you know? There\'s so much work to do!','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8004,'This blue leather does draw the eye, I know. You see, we have a great many eager recruits running around here, hunting and slaying with more enthusiasm than wisdom. One must take precautions.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8005,'I cannot aid you with further lessons: your skills have surpassed mine. Go and see the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She offers more advanced training.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8006,'A task presses upon me, but I do not have the time to take care of it myself. Can I entrust you with it?','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8007,'I do not offer apprentice training. Look for the tauren Waldor in the Wailing Caverns, here in the Barrens. He can assist you with whatever you need.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8008,'Have you come for further training? Shake the dust of the road from your garments, then, and let us get to work.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8009,'My axe has seen many battles, and I like to keep it handy. Enemy forces have fought their way into our capital several times now, but have no fear: we have always driven them back.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8010,'I cannot help you with further training: your skill at working with leather rivals my own. You should speak with Una, over there. I will vouch for your skill if need be.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8011,'You have come to me for instruction, and in return I have a favor to ask of you. See it done, and you will be rewarded.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8012,'Your skills are insufficient to learn what I teach. Try talking to Mak over there instead. He can help you out until you\'re ready for more advanced lessons.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8013,'I am pleased with your progress so far. Surely the Earth Mother has inspired your hands.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8014,'We have only a small foothold on this continent for now, but the humans can\'t fight us off forever. Then they\'ll pay for enslaving us. We\'ll cut their lying tongues out for their treachery.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8015,'I\'d train you if I could, but you\'re too much for me. Tell you what: go talk to the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She\'s got some real talent.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8016,'There\'s enough work here for an army of orcs, and most of it, only I can do. Still, there is a job I could use a hand with.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8017,'You\'ve got more guts than brains, coming to me without the proper training. Go talk to somebody closer to your skill level, like the orc Kamari, who lives in the Drag of Orgrimmar.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8018,'We\'re pretty far from anything I\'d call civilization here, at least until the Horde can send us more reinforcements. You must really like working with leather.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8019,'Am I busy? What\'s that supposed to mean? Do you think I just stand here all day, twiddling my thumbs? If you\'re here to buy something, talk to Handor.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8020,'You won\'t learn anything new from me; you know too much already. If you want more training, talk to the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. Send her my regards, eh?','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8021,'That\'s decent work, I admit. But I\'d be more impressed if you\'d handle something for me.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8022,'You can\'t study my techniques until you\'ve learned the basics. Speak with Kamari if you are interested in training.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8023,'The twists and turns of Orgrimmar are designed to thwart invaders. Can you imagine how quickly one of those puny gnomes would get lost in here? Ha! If it was lucky, I\'d track it down and keep it as a pet.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8024,'Before my death, I was a librarian; I had nothing to do with wars and plagues. I never asked to become this. On the other hand, now that my mind is my own again, I\'m not about to surrender without a fight.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8025,'I\'m pleased to say that your talents have outpaced my own. Go away now. Err, try the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She\'s very skilled, I assure you.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8026,'Yes, yes, I\'ll train you. There\'s no need to raise your voice.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8027,'If I taught novices, there\'d be a lot more students visiting me, and things would get noisy. Go talk to Dan Golthas over there. He\'s a little intense, but he means well, and he\'s a decent teacher.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8028,'I first set up shop in the Magic Quarter, but it was pretty noisy there. This is a definite improvement, barring a few persistent students who still track me down, despite the fact that I\'ve relocated.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8029,'','Elune has granted the night elves many gifts. In return, it is our responsibility to safeguard these forests from the demonic taint that the Horde always brings with it.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8030,'','Training you further is beyond my abilities. Speak to Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He is always glad to help talented students.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8031,'','I cannot leave my post here, $n, but there is a task that must be taken care of. Can I trust you to see it done?',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8032,'','I only teach students who have already mastered the basics. You must seek out the night elf Darianna in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. Her skills will be a perfect complement to yours.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8033,'','Always double-check your measurements before you begin to cut the leather. We cannot afford to waste materials.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8034,'I need a ride, Dungar!  I have important supplies to deliver!','I need a ride, Dungar!  I have important supplies to deliver!',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8035,'Do you know where I may find the Half Pendant of Aquatic Agility?','Do you know where I may find the Half Pendant of Aquatic Agility?',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8036,'Do you know where I may find the Half Pendant of Aquatic Endurance?','Do you know where I may find the Half Pendant of Aquatic Endurance?',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8037,'The waters of Westfall are where you must search, due west-northwest of where the Gold Coast Quarry meets with the shore.  An anchor shows where a boat has sunk beyond it, deep within the water.  The underwater pressure is fierce here; swimming too far will crush even the mightiest swimmer from fatigue.  $B$BLook for a natural formation to aid you, $n - a bubbly fissure is near here, offering deep-water swimmers a chance for renewed breath.\n','',0,0,0,1,0,0,0,0,0),(8038,'In the Silverpine Forest along the edges of the North Tide\'s Run, a derelict boat rests on the shore.  Out to the west of this lies what you seek; swim too far and the ocean will crush you from fatigue.  It resides on the ocean floor in a lockbox, waiting for you to claim it.$B$BYou\'ll be hard pressed to survive a dive to such depths without aid, so take heart; a bubbly fissure offers renewed breath to divers seeking this half of the pendant.  Use it wisely.','',0,0,0,1,0,0,0,0,0),(8039,'','In the northern part of Darkshore runs the Cliffspring River, flowing down from the lands now known as Felwood.  As the river flows out and empties out into the Mist\'s Edge, travel north to where the deepest parts of the ocean begin.  A stone formation that some call the Stone Claw due to its shape is where you may find what you seek.$B$BBe warned - threshers gather by the Stone Claw, and will attack those who trespass on their territory.',0,0,0,1,0,0,0,0,0),(8040,'','In the northeastern Barrens lies a pool of water sickened by pollution.  The locals call it the Sludge Fen; the Venture Company has turned the once crystal-blue waters into a mire of industrial byproducts and waste.  In the heart of this fen lies what you seek, $n.$B$BBe warned - the Venture Company does not tolerate trespassers, and they consider anyone who does not work for them as such.  You\'ll especially be a target as a protector of nature, something they vehemently oppose.',0,0,0,1,0,0,0,0,0),(8041,'The grass is soft and lush. The air is fresh, full of light and song. Everything I\'ve seen suggests that Teldrassil is a dream come true. Why, then, is my heart full of foreboding?','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8042,'You have advanced beyond my skill to teach you. Journey now to Aerie Peak in the Hinterlands and speak with the dwarf Drakk Stonehand. His work is magnificent, far better than my own.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8043,'You have demonstrated skill in learning our craft. Do you also possess the resolve to complete a mission on my behalf?','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8044,'I regret to say that I cannot aid you, $gnoble sir:gentle lady;, until you learn more of working with leather. Speak with Faldron or Darianna here instead. They can teach you the skill you require.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8045,'Do not try to force your will upon the leather. Rather, let its natural tendencies dictate what form and function it will take. This is not a battle to be won. Work with the leather, not against it.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8046,'','The needle is small, but the thread is strong, and the stitches are fine. Our pact with Thrall and the others will hold. The Horde will not be driven from these lands.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8047,'','Even my talents have a limit, and you have reached it. Congratulations, $n. Your next stop should be Camp Mojache in Feralas. The tauren Hahrana Ironhide lives there; she is renowned for her skill.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8048,'','As members of the Horde, we must contribute to our community to ensure that it continues to thrive. Thus, I am certain you will gladly aid us by undertaking a small task I have for you.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8049,'','It\'s been so long since I was a novice myself that I don\'t think I\'d be the best teacher for you. Try talking to Tarn or Mak, right over there. One of them should be able to answer your questions.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8050,'','Cairne has brought us to a land rich with possibilities for the future. We have been fortunate, and so in turn we pass on our good fortune to others. That is why I began teaching, $n.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8051,'I can make amazing things with the materials I find out here. By Muradin\'s beard, there are fantastic creatures in these hills! Go have a whack at them, $n, and bring me back some tall tales.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8052,'Och, \'twas a sad day when I realized my obsession. I woke up and found myself tannin\' before I had my first tankard of ale. Hardly even a respectable hangover! I knew then--aye, I knew!--how it was goin\' to be.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8053,'I love a good challenge; don\'t you? Aye, of course ye do. An\' that\'s why you\'re about to do exactly what I say.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8054,'I\'m not here to teach babes fresh out of the cradle. Ye\'ve nowhere near the amount of skill I require in my students. In fact, ye\'re a sad figure of a $glad:lass;, an\' I\'ll thank ye not to stand there jibber-jabberin\' at me.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8055,'','All requests for my work must be made in person by the buyer. Orwin often asks me to reconsider, but my priorities lie here. Look around you: many of these fighters rely upon me for their armor.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8056,'','I only wish I had more students like you. Not many will venture so far into enemy territory. I salute your courage.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8057,'','We cannot afford to give an inch in this war. Day and night, I create new armor, and I patch whatever can be salvaged from the old. I have no time for other tasks. Would you take care of something for me?',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8058,'','You have wasted your time and mine by coming to me for training, $n. I have no time to teach basic skills. We\'re fighting a war here, and this is one of the front lines. Don\'t return to me until you are more prepared.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8059,'I can tell that your wardrobe is in dire need of care.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8060,'I\'m a simple man who knows a few things about tailoring, but you need more assistance than I can provide. I have heard of a Night Elf who is quite an accomplished tailor. He resides in Stormwind, in the Magic District. ','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8061,'So you would like to learn a few things? I would be happy to get you started!','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8062,'Life is like a carefully woven tapestry.','',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0),(8063